fect acting at nonlinear scales, and in\nparticular is the most important mechanism in lowering the concentration of\nCold Dark Matter halos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2010 21:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2011 09:59:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
