on of the problem, establishing a simple\nrelation between both approaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2010 13:49:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Jun 2011 21:55:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-15"}
